{"tid":801835,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"凡於指定日期購買了 iPhone 8，有機會獲贈免費延長主機板保養","createTime":"2018-09-01T03:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T06:19:13.000Z","uid":155374,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"07ae842f98fccd28cc7fb3ea6fcf31db3708ff50","tid":801835,"uid":155374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:45:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Apple 已確定有少部分的 iPhone 8 裝置主機板有製造瑕疵。受影響的裝置可能會突然重新啟動、畫面凍結或無法開機。Apple 將免費維修符合資格的裝置。</span><br />\n<br />\n如果您的 iPhone 8 序號符合資格，Apple 將免費提供維修。請使用下方的序號檢查工具，查看您的裝置是否符合本計畫的資格。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋找序號很容易。查看如何尋找序號。<br />\n本計畫不包含 iPhone 8 Plus 機型和其他 iPhone 機型。<br />\n<br />\n維修程序<br />\n請選擇下面其中一個服務選項以維修您的 iPhone 8。進行任何維修服務前，我們會先檢查您的 iPhone 以確認是否符合本計畫資格。<br />\n<br />\n尋找 Apple 授權維修中心。<br />\n預約前往 Apple Store 零售店。<br />\n維修前，請將 iPhone 備份到 iTunes 或 iCloud。進一步瞭解如何準備將 iPhone 送修。<br />\n<br />\n如果您的 iPhone 8 有任何會影響此次維修的損壞情況，例如螢幕破裂，則須在接受本方案維修服務前解決該問題。在某些情況下，可能需要支付額外的維修費用。<br />\n<br />\n其他資訊<br />\nApple 可能會限制維修條件，或要求只能在原購買國家或地區接受維修。<br />\n<br />\n這項 Apple 計畫並不會延長 iPhone 8 的標準保固範圍。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">本計畫涵蓋裝置首次零售之後 3 年期間受影響的 iPhone 8 裝置。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.apple.com/hk/support/iphone-8-logic-board-replacement-program/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fsupport%2Fiphone-8-logic-board-replacement-program%2F&d=rPgQoPP2bU%2BhQE9jxV%2FwA7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=82f683b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.apple.com/hk/support/iphone-8-logic-board-replacement-program/</a>"},{"pid":"21741c1ead18a69df453063f1e9c2a12cda950dd","tid":801835,"uid":17502,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:56:50.000Z","msg":"Apple 已確定有少部分的 iPhone 8 裝置主機板有製造瑕疵，但仍然照賣，吹？"},{"pid":"7c8ffe81f3f76ddccd21be12c63c8ffe50af88ff","tid":801835,"uid":155374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21741c1ead18a69df453063f1e9c2a12cda950dd","tid":801835,"uid":17502,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:56:50.000Z","msg":"Apple 已確定有少部分的 iPhone 8 裝置主機板有製造瑕疵，但仍然照賣，吹？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:19:05.000Z","msg":"呢個優惠限定㗎，其他批次冇<br />\n<br />\n受影響設備是在 2017 年 9 月至 2018 年 3 月間，於澳洲、中國、香港、印度、日本、澳門、紐西蘭和美國所銷售。"},{"pid":"1d426d14e7a3c9bad6d0b3f7ee4dc0eb04243c6b","tid":801835,"uid":5159,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:29:33.000Z","msg":"本計畫不包含 iPhone 8 Plus 機型和其他 iPhone 機型。"},{"pid":"bb7a14fc188bab825f55df3abf68633210ea9721","tid":801835,"uid":158145,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21741c1ead18a69df453063f1e9c2a12cda950dd","tid":801835,"uid":17502,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:56:50.000Z","msg":"Apple 已確定有少部分的 iPhone 8 裝置主機板有製造瑕疵，但仍然照賣，吹？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:32:02.000Z","msg":"柒左，柒埋右"},{"pid":"e9d876972823f6f96fe888dfdff6b558a4c3240e","tid":801835,"uid":155374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1d426d14e7a3c9bad6d0b3f7ee4dc0eb04243c6b","tid":801835,"uid":5159,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:29:33.000Z","msg":"本計畫不包含 iPhone 8 Plus 機型和其他 iPhone 機型。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T12:21:57.000Z","msg":"此優惠不適用於 iPhone 8 Plus 機型和其他 iPhone 機型。"},{"pid":"a34401b6653f29b2481eb10f8f2dcc4de66814c4","tid":801835,"uid":22967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T12:24:50.000Z","msg":"柒左起碼有認數既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4dae30975882549a88da9e2975038a744ba901","tid":801835,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:19:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 標題"}]}